reviewText: Sticker on box and ad said it contained "Porky's Bear Facts". This is the reason I purchased it, but it did not in fact have this cartoon at all.

Actually, I love Porky's Railroad. But the edition I had didn't have Porky's Railroad on it!!!. There are supposed to be four cartoons on this VHS tape and there was one. Make sure "Porky's Railroad" is in fact on your VHS tape before you buyit!
